    "description": "This one's a certified banger. Warm the soul with proper hearty sausages, creamy mash and dreamy caramelised onion gravy. Serve with green peas and roasted carrots for comfort food at its feel-good best. Finish your meal with a Pots & Co Chocolate Pot.",
